    <section>
      <h2>Why Jobsolv Wins</h2>

      <h3>1. Per-Job Resume Tailoring</h3>
      <p>Indeed uses your uploaded resume for all applications with no customization. Jobsolv customizes your resume for every job, matching keywords and skills from each job description. This significantly improves ATS pass rates and interview conversion.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Generic applications get lost among hundreds of applicants → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Higher interview rates with targeted applications</p>

      <h3>2. Less Competition</h3>
      <p>Indeed has millions of active job seekers competing for the same roles. Jobsolv's specialized remote/hybrid focus means less competition per job. You're not competing against Indeed's entire user base.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Getting lost among hundreds of applicants → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Better visibility in less crowded marketplace</p>

      <h3>3. Integrated Application Platform</h3>
      <p>Job board, resume builder, tailoring, and tracking in one place. Indeed requires you to search jobs, manage applications, and track progress separately. Jobsolv streamlines the entire application process.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Managing multiple disconnected tools and processes → <strong>Outcome:</strong> One platform for browsing, tailoring, and applying</p>

      <h3>4. Specialized Remote/Hybrid Focus</h3>
      <p>Jobsolv curates remote and hybrid roles paying $100K+, updated daily. Indeed has all job types, requiring extensive filtering. Jobsolv saves time by focusing on roles that match your preferences.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Wasting time filtering through irrelevant jobs → <strong>Outcome:</strong> See only relevant remote/hybrid high-paying roles</p>

      <h3>5. ATS-Optimized Applications</h3>
      <p>Jobsolv automatically optimizes resumes for ATS systems with each tailoring. Indeed requires you to manually optimize your resume, which many users don't do effectively.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Resumes rejected by ATS before human review → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Resumes designed to pass automated filters</p>
    </section>

